{"tid":1896538,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】八鄉少年警訊中心作隔離營 區議員促徵用軍營 徐德義拒回應","createTime":"2020-02-25T07:44:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T08:59:39.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0be12ccb7bb1828d9f8c0d7b9216ab1ba66170e2","tid":1896538,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:44:38.000Z","msg":"（獨媒特約報導）武漢肺炎本地確診個案新增至74宗，疫情未有減退跡象。2月初，警方表示會借出八鄉少年警訊中心，加裝組合屋改建為武漢肺炎檢疫中心。元朗區議會召開大會討論，區議員李頌慈質疑政府未有嘗試徵用軍營作隔離營，「係咪呢啲地方代表中國嘅權力，所以政府就唔用？」食衞局副局長徐德義指，政府會優先徵用可即時使用之場所作隔離營，包括有獨立廁所的公屋單位。徐德義亦多次迴避議員追問，未有回應會否將軍營及前公務員宿舍改建為檢疫中心，並指「唔可能逐一討論不同選址嘅可能性。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1071039\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1071039&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpSfW%2F3rzywXjCQwsEwiLy3M%3D&h=12c2de8d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1071039&h=72cc17c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1071039</a>"},{"pid":"6e124cd7b9bee9e9b9f022624ed4821dc9e582e3","tid":1896538,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T08:57:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=2snho0MtSZbn8sjHWbtmpSfW%2F3rzywXjCQwsEwiLy3M%3D&h=9012059e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task</span></strong></span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"59a847009b1f48c1db9f9219d6c4d101b39222a5","tid":1896538,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T08:59:39.000Z","msg":"唔可能你老母 就算你話唔夠時間係會議講 唔撚識派文件？"}]}